FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[Address], [c].[CityName], [c].[CommunityId], [c].[CommunityName], [c].[CommunityTypeId], [c].[CreatedBy], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[FeesMonthly], [c].[GracePeriod], [c].[NoOfParkingLot], [c].[NoOfUnits], [c].[PICEmail], [c].[PICMobile], [c].[PICName], [c].[StateId], [c].[UpdatedBy], [c].[UpdatedDate], [s].[Id] AS [Id0], [s].[Name]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [r].[Id], [r].[Name], [r].[Email], [r].[BlockNo], [r].[HouseNo], [r].[Level], [r].[MaintenenceFeesCost], [r].[LotNo], [r].[NRIC], [r].[ParkingLotQty], [r].[ParkingLotNos], [r].[PhoneNo], [r].[RoadNo], [r].[CommunityId], CAST(1 AS bit) AS [c], [c].[CommunityId] AS [CommunityId0], [c].[CommunityName], [c].[FeesMonthly], [c].[Id] AS [Id0]

    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[Address], [c].[CityName], [c].[CommunityId], [c].[CommunityName], [c].[CommunityTypeId], [c].[CreatedBy], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[FeesMonthly], [c].[GracePeriod], [c].[NoOfParkingLot], [c].[NoOfUnits], [c].[PICEmail], [c].[PICMobile], [c].[PICName], [c].[StateId], [c].[UpdatedBy], [c].[UpdatedDate], [s].[Id] AS [Id0], [s].[Name]

    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[Address], [c].[CityName], [c].[CommunityId], [c].[CommunityName], [c].[CommunityTypeId], [c].[CreatedBy], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[FeesMonthly], [c].[GracePeriod], [c].[NoOfParkingLot], [c].[NoOfUnits], [c].[PICEmail], [c].[PICMobile], [c].[PICName], [c].[StateId], [c].[UpdatedBy], [c].[UpdatedDate], [s].[Id] AS [Id0], [s].[Name]

) AS [t]

    SELECT TOP(1) [r].[Id], [r].[Name], [r].[Email], [r].[BlockNo], [r].[HouseNo], [r].[Level], [r].[MaintenenceFeesCost], [r].[LotNo], [r].[NRIC], [r].[ParkingLotQty], [r].[ParkingLotNos], [r].[PhoneNo], [r].[RoadNo], [r].[CommunityId], CAST(1 AS bit) AS [c], [c].[CommunityId] AS [CommunityId0], [c].[CommunityName], [c].[FeesMonthly], [c].[Id] AS [Id0]
    FROM [Resident] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Community] AS [c] ON [r].[CommunityId] = [c].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[Id] = @__residentId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [VehicleDetails] AS [v] ON [t].[Id] = [v].[ResidentId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0]

    SELECT TOP(1) [r].[Id], [r].[Name], [r].[Email], [r].[BlockNo], [r].[HouseNo], [r].[Level], [r].[MaintenenceFeesCost], [r].[LotNo], [r].[NRIC], [r].[ParkingLotQty], [r].[ParkingLotNos], [r].[PhoneNo], [r].[RoadNo], [r].[CommunityId], CAST(1 AS bit) AS [c], [c].[CommunityId] AS [CommunityId0], [c].[CommunityName], [c].[FeesMonthly], [c].[Id] AS [Id0]
    FROM [Resident] AS [r]

) AS [t]

    SELECT TOP(1) [r].[Id], [r].[Name], [r].[Email], [r].[BlockNo], [r].[HouseNo], [r].[Level], [r].[MaintenenceFeesCost], [r].[LotNo], [r].[NRIC], [r].[ParkingLotQty], [r].[ParkingLotNos], [r].[PhoneNo], [r].[RoadNo], [r].[CommunityId], CAST(1 AS bit) AS [c], [c].[CommunityId] AS [CommunityId0], [c].[CommunityName], [c].[FeesMonthly], [c].[Id] AS [Id0]
    FROM [Resident] AS [r]
    INNER JOIN [Community] AS [c] ON [r].[CommunityId] = [c].[Id]
    WHERE [r].[Id] = @__residentId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [VehicleDetails] AS [v] ON [t].[Id] = [v].[ResidentId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Address], [t].[CityName], [t].[CommunityId], [t].[CommunityName], [t].[CommunityTypeId], [t].[CreatedBy], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[FeesMonthly], [t].[GracePeriod], [t].[NoOfParkingLot], [t].[NoOfUnits], [t].[PICEmail], [t].[PICMobile], [t].[PICName], [t].[StateId], [t].[UpdatedBy], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t].[Id0], [t].[Name], [v].[Id], [v].[Amount], [v].[ChargeTypeId], [v].[CommunityId], [v].[CreatedBy], [v].[CreatedDate], [v].[NoOfVistorParkingLot], [v].[Status], [v].[UpdatedBy], [v].[UpdatedDate]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[Address], [c].[CityName], [c].[CommunityId], [c].[CommunityName], [c].[CommunityTypeId], [c].[CreatedBy], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[FeesMonthly], [c].[GracePeriod], [c].[NoOfParkingLot], [c].[NoOfUnits], [c].[PICEmail], [c].[PICMobile], [c].[PICName], [c].[StateId], [c].[UpdatedBy], [c].[UpdatedDate], [s].[Id] AS [Id0], [s].[Name]
    FROM [Community] AS [c]
    LEFT JOIN [State] AS [s] ON [c].[StateId] = [s].[Id]
    WHERE [c].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [VisitorParkingCharge] AS [v] ON [t].[Id] = [v].[CommunityId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0]

    SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[Address], [c].[CityName], [c].[CommunityId], [c].[CommunityName], [c].[CommunityTypeId], [c].[CreatedBy], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[FeesMonthly], [c].[GracePeriod], [c].[NoOfParkingLot], [c].[NoOfUnits], [c].[PICEmail], [c].[PICMobile], [c].[PICName], [c].[StateId], [c].[UpdatedBy], [c].[UpdatedDate], [s].[Id] AS [Id0], [s].[Name]
    FROM [Community] AS [c]
    LEFT JOIN [State] AS [s] ON [c].[StateId] = [s].[Id]
    WHERE [c].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [VisitorParkingCharge] AS [v] ON [t].[Id] = [v].[CommunityId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0]
